title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 6 2022
description:
Biden's giant teleprompter is a symbol for Trojan horse presidency -- and some rooms in the White House can't be used for his appearances since teleprompter won't fit! Is Carville right about abortion motivating Democrats? Ann Coulter joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Roe v. Wade leak and why she's not worried about the abortion decision screwing up the midterms. Sunny Hostin smears black and latino Republicans.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
